{"tid":1301584,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"網上流傳 2019-2020長期抗爭時間表","createTime":"2019-07-09T16:31:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T16:33:53.000Z","uid":90601,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"cd882e020ae36e290bbb8377ed7124e3b1db9e58","tid":1301584,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:31:30.000Z","msg":"我係藍絲 絕對愛國愛黨 習大大是最好的<br />\n但聽講有班人反中亂港 專針對大日子<br />\n以下係我朋友傳俾我既<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">長期抗爭時間表</span></span></ins></strong><br />\n我貼出黎想大家有個心理準備 小心社會動亂 大家千祈唔好參加<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>10月1日：十一国慶/建党70周年<br />\n10月立會復會：國歌法 明日大愚<br />\n2019年11月區選<br />\n2020年立法會選舉</strong></ins><br />\n<br />\n有無人仲知有咩日子要補充???<br />\n<br />\n聽講仲有班黃屍整緊文宣圖<br />\n有既巴打可唔可post埋出黎 等分享俾家中長輩提醒佢地"},{"pid":"2da4094d64a909cd6b089bfbd8e6e62949c02c59","tid":1301584,"uid":200758,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:32:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AiR3F8V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAiR3F8V.jpg&h=f4a2740b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EuDmAd2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEuDmAd2.jpg&h=28455d55&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"754dac662103e826c60cefbdb77265df178afc24","tid":1301584,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:33:40.000Z","msg":"黃屍反中亂港 其心可誅!!"},{"pid":"b0a976feeafd178862e211e3a23eb7617deeb664","tid":1301584,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2da4094d64a909cd6b089bfbd8e6e62949c02c59","tid":1301584,"uid":200758,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:32:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AiR3F8V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAiR3F8V.jpg&h=f4a2740b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EuDmAd2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumb